OL,6,FHelen, 81, was hit as she crossed on a
OL,7,Fgreen pedestrian signal in Earl's
OL,8,FCourt, London, on May 10, 2023, by a
OL,9,Fmotorcycle escorting the Duchess of
OL,10,FEdinburgh. She died in hospital two
OL,11,Fweeks later.
OL,13,FLast Thursday, after two hours of
OL,14,Fdeliberation, a jury at the Old Bailey
OL,15,Facquitted PC Christopher Harrison, 68,
OL,16,Fof causing death by careless driving.
OL,18,FThe verdict has left Helen's relatives
OL,19,Ffeeling "cheated", "devastated" and
OL,20,Fhas knocked their faith in the justice
OL,21,Fsystem.
