OL,6,FSpeaking exclusively to ITV News,
OL,7,FHelen's brother Chris Holmes and
OL,8,Fgranddaughter Kelly Williams said the
OL,9,Fdecision effectively shifted
OL,10,Fresponsibility onto Helen herself -
OL,11,Feven though the pedestrian signal was
OL,12,Fgreen.
OL,14,F"If the policeman is not guilty of
OL,15,Fcareless driving, then she's guilty of
OL,16,Fcareless walking," Chris said.
OL,18,F"I feel there's a terrible injustice."
