OL,6,FHe told jurors Helen "just appeared"
OL,7,Fin front of him.
OL,9,FThe family reject this explanation
OL,10,Fentirely.
OL,12,F"You should have seen her," Chris said.
OL,14,FKelly added: "He went through at speed
OL,15,Fand smashed my nan to pieces."
OL,17,FWhen the verdict was announced,
OL,18,Fsomeone in the public gallery shouted:
OL,19,F"You ruined our family with no
OL,20,Fconsequences", a sentiment Chris said
OL,21,Fsummed up their feelings.
